img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a648af514d9f59373b1d3c18dda71971970188","tid":430683,"uid":131671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成船都係學生 好似秋季旅行 佢地帶晒行李 應該過埋夜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夜晚鼠入佢地個營到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地應該唔係住營 因為差唔多成百人 有老師帶<br />\n<br />\n附圖1200+400 定食<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/182814_622025e1d96c9b3b4d2451e2bf3c1c5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F182814_622025e1d96c9b3b4d2451e2bf3c1c5a.jpg&h=4ec4f8db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1efb83ad7e510e26f6bb97f68bf8325579a70221","tid":430683,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:29:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> off topic <br />\n啱啱去福岡附近個相島(貓島)，見到有個香港女仔獨遊so pure so true，到咗之後一開始咁啱玩埋同一堆貓，之後就唔見咗佢。<br />\n後尾上船又見到佢，見佢恰晒眼瞓咁諗住一陣應該都係搭jr，一陣先聊佢，點知上咗接駁巴士發現佢係上西鐵接駁巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後只係傾咗不足五句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再見喇</blockquote><br />\n我試過去西大山站都撞到個獨遊既香港女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9273378454fa181d9b1abf13bb8bd427e29762","tid":430683,"uid":131671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:35:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> off topic <br />\n啱啱去福岡附近個相島(貓島)，見到有個香港女仔獨遊so pure so true，到咗之後一開始咁啱玩埋同一堆貓，之後就唔見咗佢。<br />\n後尾上船又見到佢，見佢恰晒眼瞓咁諗住一陣應該都係搭jr，一陣先聊佢，點知上咗接駁巴士發現佢係上西鐵接駁巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後只係傾咗不足五句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再見喇</blockquote><br />\n諗左成日都唔知點應你 總之加油啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都好鍾意玩貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723ecc790f08c95ddb3b57cd1f4aa1e2a0fb124b","tid":430683,"uid":17100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:32:23.000Z","msg":"Lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beba94e83bca3ba06dfd5ec3c649739168ad3dd4","tid":430683,"uid":131671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T09:50:16.000Z","msg":"一條友行左2日山 終於番到有wifi地方<br />\n我係由紀元杉開始 -》淀川登山口(1380m) -〉宮之浦岳（1936m) （由紀元杉到宮之浦岳山頂大約用左5-6hr） -》新高塚小屋（ 山頂行2.5hr倒到）訓一晚 -〉繩文杉 （小屋行約1.5hr）-》荒川登山口 （繩文行3.5-4hr到）-〉坐巴士走 <br />\n<br />\n成個行程大約26公里 <br />\n去到紀元杉有2個台灣女仔話沉日行完 冇住一晚 <br />\n我諗輕裝得既 佢地應該坐最早果班巴士<br />\n<br />\n而我就比個旅館老闆高估左 佢指左8:40分 由碼頭開出 去到Gochomae呢個站再轉車上紀元杉 上到去都10:30。<br />\n<br />\n換言之 你睇番行程上面個時間  我影完紀元杉都差唔多10點45分  5.5hr+2.5hr =行8hr到小屋  我行果日645先行到小屋 個天都就黑晒 最後500m要開燈行<br />\n<br />\n建議如果大家要行宮之浦山 最好就早D  而且上山路唔易 某d位要拉繩爬 手腳並用先上倒 <br />\n<br />\n跟絲帶行就實冇錯  跟牌行 其實路都係得一條 有D似路非路行10秒 你已經知行錯  <br />\n<br />\n水方面我帶得2L幾 行全程一定唔夠 山上面 有幾個水位比你斟水飲 全部都溪水黎 我見D日本人都就咁飲 我都飲左1L 暫時都未有事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後若果真係要訓一晚高塚小屋 記得記得要帶睡袋同軟墊 因為木板好硬 加上得10度左右氣溫  冇睡袋係一定凍到眼光光 好似我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/174948_5509527611fb68cbace22be46195e190.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F174948_5509527611fb68cbace22be46195e190.jpg&h=4cb52db6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/174950_5550a3ffd8cbf842cf92a387c41cc333.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F174950_5550a3ffd8cbf842cf92a387c41cc333.jpg&h=6854a023&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/174953_97c14e8da7829d5a7365dd99c5ccf682.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F174953_97c14e8da7829d5a7365dd99c5ccf682.jpg&h=e1b72f56&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/174956_7c37d31e9adf70542a59f9d1d44df635.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F174956_7c37d31e9adf70542a59f9d1d44df635.jpg&h=f2a9dbf8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/174959_504dc1880894cbe645590b535e98d9e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F174959_504dc1880894cbe645590b535e98d9e3.jpg&h=1484b48e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"daad4f1f88cd0fe3aa820e09e77177c67a2f3679","tid":430683,"uid":131671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T09:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/175302_6b388977926fe3aac6e868714f44a37a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F175302_6b388977926fe3aac6e868714f44a37a.jpg&h=b77fcceb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/175305_70c0162943aeb3801d7c2e753d69b9db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F175305_70c0162943aeb3801d7c2e753d69b9db.jpg&h=5240292b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/175308_7a0e6328ccb31638343fdc0655ebf63a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F175308_7a0e6328ccb31638343fdc0655ebf63a.jpg&h=a72e2ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/175311_278d973a942d100907b84c9062c6ba08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F175311_278d973a942d100907b84c9062c6ba08.jpg&h=44a6da8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/175313_d8c10ee0f1a25a72bf5d4792ec231433.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F175313_d8c10ee0f1a25a72bf5d4792ec231433.jpg&h=60b79af4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"846c85d994c9b96dbea756ba7d4aa07435d0cf17","tid":430683,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T09:55:09.000Z","msg":"Jetfoil都要兩個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6713e86448f2df5e21b3f5e3d1d9698aef7adaf1","tid":430683,"uid":131671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Jetfoil都要兩個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係阿 都算幾遠"},{"pid":"5c07e57e84fd8516f2859ddfaeff578a3edfcf9b","tid":430683,"uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:20:49.000Z","msg":"巴絲打你地知道俾人玩完，呃飲呃食最後對方話同你分手，係咪覺得好無助呢？<br />\n唔知你地分左手幾耐呢？你地依家覺得個心好撚痛？定仲覺得自己有希望佢會返黎？<br />\n<br />\n我都明白點解會有呢d咁嘅情況，係因為你根本就唔相信呢個係事實，你唔相信一個人，可以琴日仲對住你講I love you,今日就話我地唔岩/我唔夠愛你呢d借口同你分手。<br />\n<br />\n但我想講！醒下啦！我今日就係要話俾你地知夠鐘起身啦！<br />\n<br />\n我一個月前同個賤男散左，我個陣成個腦一片空白。我接受唔到一個人一日前仲好開心話自動請纓黎接我收工仲好sweet咁，過多就話同我散？<br />\n我過左個一個星期我個人完全崩潰，直頭係成個人癡線。過左一個星期我再搵返佢。冷淡到仆街。我仲傻到以為佢有乜苦衷<br />\n過多排，我發現佢Ig block 左我。但係已經冇左follow 大家。<br />\n<br />\n個一刻醒撚左,個腦就係得呢堆字:傻系你俾人玩啦！<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母呀？我依家殺撚左你全家呀？定我一出世就欠撚左你呀臭鳩？<br />\n我拎個心出黎對你架你老母，你好玩唔玩玩人感情？咁撚多人係要玩我？？？<br />\n我屌你老母仆街呀！<br />\n你知唔知你有幾hurt我呀？<br />\n我真係好撚想你死撚左去 <br />\n我都未block你Ig 啦<br />\n你竟然block 我！？<br />\n<br />\n諗返起其實你條臭鳩都死有餘辜<br />\n未同我一齊個陣你同其他女出街我理唔到你因爲我唔係你邊個。但屌你老母呃9我同男人出街做乜春呀？？？<br />\n同我一齊又搵ex 我屌你老母呀！<br />\n<br />\n仲有，做男人做到好似你咁撚樣，我係你就死撚左去咪留係到做害人精啦！<br />\n我未見過男人好似你咁撚賤格<br />\n係人面前數衰自己個ex 話人去有幾撚癡線<br />\n扮撚曬可憐咁 cheap撚到你<br />\n等d女上當。一齊左之後又扮曬嘢帶你見屋企人朋友。等人覺得安心啦，跟住就一嘢狠狠咁飛左人。之後就再loop過，係另一條女就數撚臭我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你老母闃閪！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你咁撚識扮嘢去拎視帝啦冚家剷！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲打，憎一個ex唔等於你未放底佢。因為憎已經同愛係唔同嘅事。如果你愛佢你係會想佢幸福，想佢過得好。但係憎，你係想佢死，想佢日日都折墮到仆街。愛係祝福，憎係詛咒。<br />\n<br />\n至於點解咁憎一個人，係覺得自己好唔抵。<br />\n愛情嘅付出，係唔應該要求有回報，但冇回報唔等於我地要得到更差嘅對待。<br />\n拎個心對對方好 點知對方就咁對你<br />\n個感覺就好似俾人有心有目的咁傷害，但你明明冇得罪過佢。<br />\n良心當狗肺。<br />\n人可以愛錯3.5個仆街<br />\n但唔可以愛同一個仆街3.5次。<br />\n<br />\n被人傷害嘅巴絲打，愛情路上。共勉之。<br />\n如果你地憎唔落個ex，我寧願你地日日上黎叫春又好，煩住身邊d人都好。都千其唔好俾個臭鳩同臭閪知道你仲叫春。唔好揭瘡疤俾仆街睇。因為佢地唔會同情你，反手係個傷口就灑鹽。<br />\n<br />\n至於同我一樣，依家好撚憎ex嘅巴絲打<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家同我一齊屌爆佢地老母！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依家我日日都祈禱:<br />\n希望你個死仆街仔幫臭雞埋單！<br />\n臭鳩臭閪絕配，別散廢事害人。<br />\n兩人天地長久，百年閪鳩好合！<br />\n揸車需炒車死，撘車必撞車死！<br />\n天下玩感情者，屌曬你地老母！<br />\n你地呢班仆街冚家剷約埋一齊去食屎啦！<br />\n食完就去仆街死啦！完全唔撚明白仲可以咁撚無恥咁生存！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n愛情其實係一件好美好嘅事。千其唔好因爲呢d仆街地令到自己對愛情失去信心，唔值得。你記住，做個更好嘅自己，仲要好好咁愛錫自己。從失敗中吸引教訓。去迎接下一個更好嘅佢。俾人玩俾人帽會覺得心痛，係因為你係一個人，你有感覺，你會念舊，所以你會覺得傷心。而個班係禽獸，根本人同禽獸係唔可以談戀愛架！做個有自信嘅人呀一定要！因為有自信嘅你真係好靚好有型呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家好憎佢，所以我日日都想佢仆街死！我要用想佢仆街嘅動力 去成為更好的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後，我深信你班仆街唔還債還死都後悔死呀！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/013402_dbcc6975aa0454c9bb3ba3af84865289.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F013402_dbcc6975aa0454c9bb3ba3af84865289.jpg&h=5808b819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾兩首歌大家聽下啦，唔好聽傷心情歌啦。呢次根本唔叫失戀，係個天放你走，因為你值得更好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oyEuk8j8imI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoyEuk8j8imI&d=VL92U77%2BVVEkm1aF96RxY54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=bfba1e19\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oyEuk8j8imI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kTHNpusq654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkTHNpusq654&d=VL92U77%2BVVEkm1aF96RxY54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=093d73d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kTHNpusq654</a>"},{"pid":"6a60ba75871043d43fbc57967a44f92eae144d6e","tid":430683,"uid":36565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:26:37.000Z","msg":"繩文杉即日來回幾好行 嗰陣撞正兩三團鬼妹架妹一齊行 大家share好西睇wilson株影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c601b969091ff81aae194cfe14c983c6160d27f","tid":430683,"uid":134799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T11:02:03.000Z","msg":"真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲樹木好養眼"},{"pid":"f263739d0d58aa3aa3cf3bd91bdec0b97b541ee9","tid":430683,"uid":131671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T11:23:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>繩文杉即日來回幾好行 嗰陣撞正